  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd  \u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bail for unsportsmanlike conduct in uniform",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kambalai District Court Magistrate Namal Perera has released an ex-naval soldier on bail of one lakh rupees for using navy uniform and getting 45 liters of petrol.",
        "Only one naval officer from Kampala-Angammana area has been released on bail.",
        "It is learned that the suspect came to the fuel station located on Kampala-Kandy road a few days back in a navy uniform and got 45 liters of petrol in a can saying that he needed it for a boat belonging to the navy.",
        "Following a complaint received by the Officer-in-Charge of the Talat Oya Naval Camp regarding the suspect violating the Naval Code of Conduct and obtaining fuel for his own use in uniform, he informed the Kampala police.",
        "Following this, the police arrested the suspect and produced him before Kambalay District Court Magistrate Namal Perera."
      ],
